   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:03.06" end="00:00:05.56" region="speaker">Here you can edit your Point of Contact&apos;s e-mail</p>
         <p begin="00:00:05.56" end="00:00:06.80" region="speaker">address.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.80" end="00:00:09.70" region="speaker">Enter the new e-mail address.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:09.70" end="00:00:13.46" region="speaker">The &quot;Point of Contact,&quot; &quot;Telephone&quot;, &quot;Fax&quot;, &quot;URL&quot;,</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.46" end="00:00:16.33" region="speaker">and &quot;Contract date&quot; fields become editable after</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.33" end="00:00:18.63" region="speaker">selecting the corresponding &quot;Mod Type&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.63" end="00:00:21.13" region="speaker">from the &apos;select mod type&apos; screen.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:21.13" end="00:00:23.66" region="speaker">When you are finished click &quot;Save&quot; and continue.</p>
